                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "d89a14f15ede4ddca6df5",
                    "stepText": "Now, we need to establish how much heat is generated in the extension cord. Which formula relates the heat produced in a resistor to the current through it and its resistance?",
