                    "stepText": "Great, now that you have the appropriate formula, use it to calculate the current flowing through the plumber's body when the mains voltage is $!$240\\,\\mathrm{V}$!$ and the resistance of wet skin is $!$1000\\,\\Omega$!$. Compute the numerical result.",
